<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>New Reply Notification</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      /* Add your custom CSS styles here */
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #fafafa;
        color: #222;
      }

      a {
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 1.25;
      }

      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      table td {
        vertical-align: top;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>New Reply Notification</h1>
    <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
    <p>
      We are pleased to inform you that a new reply has been added to your question in the course
      content.
    </p>
    <p>Question Title: <%= title %></p>
    <p>Please log in to the course platform to view the reply and continue the discussion.</p>
    <p>Thank you for using our platform!</p>
  </body>
</html>
